data.description: You'll enjoy the easy living this gated condo community has to offer. From the moment you arrive to your home, you're greeted with new carpet, fresh paint, and vinyl plank flooring throughout. The open living, dining, & kitchen area has abundant natural lighting, & the north-facing balcony is perfect for grilling in the evenings or enjoying your morning coffee. En-Suite Bathroom and walk-in closet in the primary bedroom. New furnace and refrigerated air units in 2022. Your finished 1 car garage has abundant extra storage.The Oso Park Community is seconds away from Oso Grande Park, one of the nicest tree-lined public parks in the city w/ immaculate mountain views. Also across the street is CNM's Montoya Campus. Bikeability is unmatched, w/ bike trails right outside the community walls.
